item.title: CVE-2021-34632|2024-08-04T00:19:47.924Z -- seo%20backlinks -- seo%20backlinks
item.description: The SEO Backlinks WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Cross-Site Request Forgery via the loc_config function found in the ~/seo-backlinks.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 4.0.1.
